<sect1 id="Documentation_Structure" role="nobrk">
  <!-- DNT-Start --><title>Documentation Structure</title><!-- DNT-End -->

  <!-- DNT-Start --><para>This manual documents the Enterprise Control Language (ECL). ECL has
  been designed specifically for working with huge sets of data. This book is
  designed to be both a learning tool and a reference work and is divided into
  the following sections:</para><!-- DNT-End -->

  <informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec align="left" colwidth="122.40pt" />

      <colspec />

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold">ECL Basics</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Addresses the fundamental concepts of <!-- DNT-Start -->ECL<!-- DNT-End -->.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold">Expressions and
          Operators</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines available operators and their expression evaluation
          precedence.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold">Value
          Types</emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Introduces data types and type casting.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold">Record Structures and
          Files</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Introduces the <!-- DNT-Start -->RECORD<!-- DNT-End --> structure, <!-- DNT-Start -->DATASET<!-- DNT-End -->, and <!-- DNT-Start -->INDEX<!-- DNT-End -->.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold">Alien Data
          Types</emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines the <!-- DNT-Start -->TYPE<!-- DNT-End --> structure and the functions it may
          use.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis
          role="bold">Natural Language Parsing
          Support</emphasis></emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines the patterns and functions the <!-- DNT-Start -->PARSE<!-- DNT-End --> function may
          use.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold">Reserved
          Keywords</emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines special-use <!-- DNT-Start -->ECL<!-- DNT-End --> keywords not elsewhere
          defined.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis
          role="bold">Special
          Structures</emphasis></emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines the <!-- DNT-Start -->TRANSFORM<!-- DNT-End -->, <!-- DNT-Start -->MACRO<!-- DNT-End -->, and other structures and their
          use.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis
          role="bold">Built-In Functions and
          Actions</emphasis></emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines the functions and actions available as part of the
          language.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis
          role="bold">Workflow
          Services</emphasis></emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines the job execution/process control aspects of
          <!-- DNT-Start -->ECL<!-- DNT-End -->.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis
          role="bold">Templates</emphasis></emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines the <!-- DNT-Start -->ECL<!-- DNT-End --> Template commands.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis role="bold">External
          Services</emphasis></emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

          <entry>Defines the <!-- DNT-Start -->SERVICE<!-- DNT-End --> structure and its use.</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>
</sect1>
